data.title: Anita Björk
data.text:
AKA Anita Barbro Kristina Björk

Born: 25-Apr-1923

Birthplace: Tällberg, Dalarna, Sweden

Died: 24-Oct-2012

Location of death: Stockholm, Sweden

Cause of death: unspecified

Gender: Female

Race or Ethnicity: White

Sexual orientation: Straight

Occupation: Actor

Nationality: Sweden

Executive summary: Miss Julie

Husband: Stig Dagerman (m. 1953, d. 4-Nov-1954 suicide, one daughter)

Boyfriend: Graham Greene (novelist)

Conservatory: Kungliga Dramatiska Teaterns Elevskola

Miss Julie (6-Apr-1951)
